    {
      "useBottomMargin": false,
      "markdown": "Sometimes someone gets hold of your phone and starts browsing through your private content out of curiosity.\n\nPMP helps protect your privacy with a single tap.\n\n### Main Features\n- Instantly hide all photos using a Control Center module.\n- Hide Hidden and Recently Deleted albums.\n- Restrict access to recently captured photos from the Camera app.\n- Quickly restore access whenever needed.\n\n### Notice\n- Face ID, Touch ID, or a passcode must be enabled to use this tweak.\n- On iOS 15/16.x, a respring is required after adding the module to Control Center.",
